  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Italian (Arts)              : Medieval ideas, attitudes and behaviour surrounding love as represented in literature: readings will include excerpts from early Italian love lyrics, Dante's Vita Nuova, Petrarch's Canzoniere, Boccaccio's Decameron.          </p>

