  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Italian (Arts)              : A study of Italian prose fiction and non-fiction in the context of some of the events and issues that marked these years: the aftermath of Fascism, the economic boom, terrorism, the Mafia, the North-South question.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
